I am disappointed to learn the hemp tees will not been restocked by our shirt printers, at least anytime soon that I can tell, and even more bummed that I didn’t get to tell y’all to get your orders in before they were totally sold out! I ordered a batch of shirts for myself and wanted to post this with an alert that some sizes were already gone, so have a look and order what you can, but by the time these arrived and I put together this clip the distributors have sold out of hemp tees entirely.
It’s such an honor to get hemp into your closet, and something I’ve been proud to do in tons of ways for about 10 years now! If you’ve been here for the journey you’ve seen this situation before, as hemp tees in a variety of sizes and colors are not the easiest to source, and even when we secure a great supply, it isn’t indefinite.
We will be looking for new suppliers of course, but this is a huge setback as the dropshipping we had in place allowed us to offer a range of colors, sizes, and multiple prints all at once, something we cannot afford the space to stock at home. I’m hopeful our distributor will restock hemp tees in the future, but without any specific timeline from them I’m left just to share the bad news that we are currently out of tees.
